importFromFile

public StratmasObject importFromFile(String fileName)
Imports units from an IF2 project. Sets the units' identifier, symbolIDCode and subunits attributes. Asks the user for an affiliation faction and initializes the remaining attributes with their default values.

Parameters:
fileName - The name of the file to import from. '
Returns:
A StratmasObject representing the unit (hierarchy) imported or null if the file did not contain any importable objects.
